Path: godot/classes/class_ikmodifier3d.rst  
Summary: Overview of IKModifier3D class methods for managing settings and resetting the modifier.  

- clear_settings (void): Removes all settings from the modifier.  
- get_setting_count (int): Returns the number of settings currently configured. const.  
- reset (void): Resets the modifier to its default state.  
- set_setting_count (void): Sets the number of settings. Parameters: count (int).
